Andrew (Andy) Laudato 

		
		CIO, 

	
		 Brookdale Senior Living Inc. 	

 
Last Updated: 10/30/2016 



Executive Summary
Andrew Laudato is Chief Information Officer of Brookdale Senior Living, a role he assumed in October 2016. Most recently he served as the Senior Vice President and Chief Information Officer of Pier 1 Imports. Laudato Joined Pier 1 Imports in 2000 as a Vice President in the Information Services Division. Prior joining Pier 1 Imports he  
Personal Attributes and Interests

Laudato is passionate about retail and technology and using the latter to improve the former.
He enjoys cycling 
Current Focus

Operational strategy:CEO Andy Smith told analysts in August 2016, "Our plan is based on leveraging both the enormous market opportunity that exists for Brookdale and our unmatched platform fo 
Biographical Highlights

A native of Mentor, Ohio, Laudato holds a BS degree in computer information systems from the DeVry University (1984-1990).
He is  a certified Project Management Profess 
Other Boards and Organizations

Former Chairman, CIO Council, National Retail Federation (NRF)
Former Member, Board of Directors, Boys & Girls Clubs of America 
 





